# Currency Converter

A modern and responsive Currency Converter web application that provides real-time exchange rates for multiple international currencies. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript using a live Exchange Rate API.

---

## Preview

> 

![Currency Converter Screenshot](assets/screenshot.png)

---

## Live Demo

https://haris786-currency-converter.vercel.app/
---

##  Features

-  Convert between 150+ currencies
-  Real-time exchange rates
-  One-click currency swap
-  Clean and modern user interface
-  Fully responsive design
-  Fast conversion results
-  Glassmorphism design
-  Smooth animations
-  Automatic exchange rate updates
-  Deployed on Vercel

---

##  Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- ExchangeRate API
- Font Awesome

---

